{"tid":2303791,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人後悔過轉工？","createTime":"2020-11-28T08:37:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T19:37:26.000Z","uid":126831,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c55cbd607c3660b7013552fc0b2c68eecd3a14fd","tid":2303791,"uid":126831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T08:37:43.000Z","msg":"畢業一年。前一份人工低 工時長 地方西，同埋明知冇心做果行，唯一係人事幾唔錯。<br />\n到轉工搵份新工以為會好d，點知仲差左。<br />\n人工叫acceptable,發覺做ge野直頭反感（先前都唔知）,果時成日以為轉工所有野都變好。<br />\n而家成日安慰自己，即使冇搵到份新工都實會辭職<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91504008abe187b47f51ffb2808d76bb9811a520","tid":2303791,"uid":288351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T08:46:32.000Z","msg":"有, 不過無得後悔, 只好向前看."},{"pid":"6c4a1c70c8a5f729138954e1f7eb122665e14e0e","tid":2303791,"uid":356930,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T08:49:15.000Z","msg":"冇，好彩轉咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然人工低咗<br />\n但做得冇乜壓力<br />\n公司又有飯卷canteen<br />\n慳番幾千<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但依家canteen好多人，冇位食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c9ff04f648e2492fb84eebcfac93b171ecdd4f9","tid":2303791,"uid":357936,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T08:53:44.000Z","msg":"人生幾十年，唔洗咁在意一兩份工，見工同辭職都好閒。最重要係你自己對市場有無價值。"},{"pid":"4503ef7675416ac3d2c5a51919f6055cb909bfe7","tid":2303791,"uid":52972,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T08:54:59.000Z","msg":"有， 由5日半轉左6日。 以為差唔係好多， 點知完全係2個世界。 星期六半日返去上2個鐘網就撇， 下晝可以訓覺行街。 返成日一個禮拜好難挨。"},{"pid":"ce662ab98383ec833d8138f77bbc8734d587dfca","tid":2303791,"uid":126831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91504008abe187b47f51ffb2808d76bb9811a520","tid":2303791,"uid":288351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T08:46:32.000Z","m